Hotel East Park Inn Karol Bagh Delhi
About Hotel: Situated in New Delhi, 4 km from Gurudwara Bangla Sahib, East Park Inn features accommodation with a shared lounge, free private parking, a terrace and a restaurant. This 4-star hotel offers a business centre and a concierge service. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi. The hotel provides an ironing service, as well as business facilities like fax and photocopying.... Hotel East Park Inn Karol Bagh Delhi

Address Park, 885, near, E Park Rd, near Ajmal Khan Road, beside Maruti Showroom, Karol Bagh, New Delhi, Delhi 110005
